Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  是琳達的戒指\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, that's Linda's ring, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那死者就是琳達·帕弗瑞\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So it is Linda Parfrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何要棄尸于蟲箱里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why dump a body into a beetle tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博物館安保措置不佳\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The museum doesn't have great security,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也沒到能隨隨便便把尸體運出去的地步\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but it's not the kind of place you can sneak a body out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非尸體小到能裝進行李袋\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Unless you make it small enough to fit in a duffel bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇手是在等蟲子將尸體啃食至\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So the killer was waiting for the bugs to eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩骨架  然后再偷運出去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}down to the skeleton so they could sneak it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能  我們在箱子里發現了一件科學器械\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Possibly. Uh, we found a scientific tool in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能是兇器\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It could be the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇手也許也是一名科學家\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So the killer's probably another scientist then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是博物館的工作人員\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Or someone that works at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次看見琳達是什么時候\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When was Linda last seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳達已經失蹤好幾星期了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Linda's been missing a couple weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家以為她是去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}People thought she was out camping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約塞米蒂國家公園做什么研究去了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}near Yosemite doing some kind of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后來有人注意到她的車停在校園里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then someone noticed her car was on campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才意識到她失蹤了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and they realized she was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰填的失蹤人口報告\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who filed the missing persons report?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索尼亞·基德博士\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dr. Sonia Kidd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是校生物系主任\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Head of the Biology Department at the university
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是琳達的顧問\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and Linda's adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字聽起來很耳熟\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Her name sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她寫過幾本書\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, she's written a couple books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流行科學讀物  有一本叫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Popular science stuff. One's called
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《天生殺手:謀殺的進化根源》\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Natural born killers: The evolutionary roots of murder."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣  我和簡去找她談談\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cute. Jane and I will go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳達在博物館有間辦公室\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And, uh, Linda had an office here at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和周去查看一下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You and Cho check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到  頭兒\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以為她在山里迷路了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We thought she was lost in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到她一直都在這里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But she was here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直太可怕了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's too horrible for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她研究什么  研究哪種動物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What did she study? What kind of animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么關系嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人會因為偶然而選擇其終身事業\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Nobody picks what they dedicate their life to by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是有原因的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It says something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我研究靈長類動物大腦\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I study primate brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能說明我是怎樣的人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What does that say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有一些陰暗的思想\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You have dark thoughts inside your head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你覺得它們很正常很自然\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that you want to believe are normal and natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然它們確實是那樣\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Which they are, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳達是研究鳥類的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Linda was an ornithologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的博士生項目是研究北撲翅鴷的飲食\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Her doctorate was on the diet of the northern flicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北撲翅鴷是一種啄木鳥\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A kind of woodpecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啄木鳥十分執著\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tenacious.
